summary:
Kurono: There you have it. Another brash, young upstart destined to surpass his aging mentor.
Chisaki: Is the commentary still...
body:
Kurono: There you have it. Another brash, young upstart destined to surpass his aging mentor.
Chisaki: Is the commentary still necessary?
Kurono: It helps me feel in control during a frankly insane situation.
Mimic: I like talking this way 'cause it makes everything sound important. "Baloney trampoline."
